comments.content:
You can't use aggregate functions in WHERE. WHERE filters individual rows BEFORE grouping. You need HAVING, which filters AFTER grouping.

SELECT department, AVG(salary) AS avg_salary FROM employees GROUP BY department HAVING AVG(salary) > 80000;

WHERE = pre-group filter. HAVING = post-group filter. Tattoo it somewhere.

